St. Francis Xavier High School is a private, Roman Catholic high school in Sumter, South Carolina.It is run independent of the Roman Catholic Diocese of Charleston.

Background
St. Francis Xavier High School opened in 1997 after just a few months of planning.It opened just months after the announced closing of Sumter Catholic High School in 1997. ;;

